Package org.openbel.framework.common.protonetwork.model

Contains the proto network object model.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AnnotationDefinitionTable AnnotationDefinitionTable holds the document annotation definitions.
AnnotationDefinitionTable.TableAnnotationDefinition TableAnnotationDefinition encapsulates a document's annotation definition.
AnnotationValueTable AnnotationValueTable holds the unique annotation value Strings.
AnnotationValueTable.TableAnnotationValue  
DocumentTable DocumentTable holds the document header information.
DocumentTable.DocumentHeader DocumentHeader holds the document header properties
NamespaceTable NamespaceTable holds the namespaces seen from documents.
NamespaceTable.TableNamespace Table namespace encapsulates a document namespace.
ParameterTable ParameterTable holds the parameter values for terms.
ParameterTable.TableParameter  
ProtoEdgeTable ProtoEdgeTable defines a symbol table to hold proto edges for the proto network.
ProtoEdgeTable.TableProtoEdge ProtoEdgeTable.TableProtoEdge defines the container object for a proto network edge.
ProtoNetwork ProtoNetwork encapsulates *Table objects.
ProtoNodeTable ProtoNodeTable defines the symbol table to hold proto nodes for the proto network.
SkinnyUUID A 'skinny' form of a UUID that stores only the most and least significant bits allowing the memory requirement of each UUID to be reduced.
StatementAnnotationMapTable StatementAnnotationMapTable holds the index mapping from statement id to annotation definition / value index pairs.
StatementAnnotationMapTable.AnnotationPair AnnotationPair represents an integer pair of annotation definition id and an annotation value id.
StatementTable StatementTable holds the statement values.
StatementTable.TableStatement TableStatement holds the statement values.
TermParameterMapTable TermParameterMapTable holds the index mapping between term values and parameter index values.
TermTable TermTable holds the term values for statements.
 

Exception Summary
ProtoNetworkError A BEL error indicating a processing error occurred for a proto-network.
